by 6%<br>when their HP is 80% or above.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span><span>Poison = Team Strength +10%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Buffs the entire team\'s strength by 10%<br>for 10 seconds upon successfully poisoning<br>an enemy. After activating, this ability will<br>not activate again for five seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/19f5e640f779cde1b60a70eedaaca10e2.png\\"><\/span><span>Bog Res +100%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to bog by 100%.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/d3edea4a52a651ab75575f278704b8a82.png\\"><\/span><span>Poisoned Punisher +30%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases damage to poisoned enemies by 30%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\n<div class=\\"summonPickUp\\">\\n<div class=\\"imageStatusWrap\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"mainImage\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/52bf50077eabdd629658e0b254fe608e.png\\"><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"status\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Stats<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"param\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"lv\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Lv<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>80<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li><li class=\\"type\\"><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/5d54775020f2b8c24e8e1d445b58d2ad2.png\\"><\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li class=\\"skill\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>10<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\"base under\\">\\